title.narrative: Nigeria Electricity and Gas Improvement Project (NEGIP)

description.narrative: The development objectives of the Project are to: (i) improve the availability and reliability of gas supply to increase power generation in existing public sector power plants; and (ii) improve the power network#s capacity and efficiency to transmit and distribute quality electricity to the consumers.

condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :FA 3.01 | Description :The Recipient declares its committment to the Objectives of the Project | Due Date:23-Jul-2010

Finance Agreement :FA Schedule 2 - Section 1- B1 | Description :The Recipient shall onlend the proceeds of the financing to theProject Implementing Entity under a subsidiary agreement entered into between the recipient and the Project Implementing Entity |Due Date :23-Jul-2010

Finance Agreement :FA Schedule 2 - Section 2 - B2 | Description :The Recipient shall cause the Project Implementining Entity tosubmit audited financial statements for the Project to the Association not later than six months after the end of each financialyear. Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :FA-Schedule 1 - A2 | Description :The Recipient shall (a) maintain ERSU and (b) cause Project ImplementingEntity to maintain PMU through the implementation of the Project | Frequency :Yearly
